----------------------------------------------------------------------
TRYING THE EXAMPLE PROGRAMS

This directory contains a few example programs to get you started with
mGTK.  In order to try the example programs, issue the following
commands

Using Moscow ML:
----------------

(1) Build mGTK (just type make in mgtk dir)

(2) make mosml 

(3) set an environment variable:
    Unix:
      export MGTKHOME=~/mgtk-pre-0.93  (when using bash)
      setenv MGTKHOME ~/mgtk-pre-0.93  (when using [t]csh)

    Windows:
      set MGTKHOME=\mgtk-pre-0.93

    OR

    copy $MGTKHOME/mgtk.so to the current dir. 

(4) Run an example.  For instance 
      ./signup


Using MLton:
------------

(1) make mlton

(2) Run an example.  For instance 
      ./signup-mlton




See NOTES for more information about the examples.

Enjoy!

